
About LAN Messenger
===================

This software is a very basic instant messaging application, meant to be ran
between machines connected to a LAN.


Compiling and installing
========================

Just use make:

$ make

If everything goes well, the server and client binaries will be placed in
build/lanmessenger_server and build/lanmessenger .

There is no make install target atm.


